  "title": "How capital allocation can rebalance capitalism in a changing world",
  "published_date": null,
  "author": "authorsalutation:|authorfirstname:Courtney|authorlastname:Rickert McCaffrey|authorjobtitle:EY-Parthenon Global Geostrategy Insights Leader; Director, Global Thematic Insights, Ernst & Young LLP|authorurl:https://www.ey.com/en_om/people/courtney-rickert-mccaffrey",
